OL,3,CJersey's migrant workers are at risk
OL,4,Cof being 'kicked into servitude'
OL,6,FSome migrant workers in Jersey are
OL,7,Fbeing "kicked into servitude",
OL,8,Faccording to a local deputy.
OL,10,FBeatriz Poree's comments come after
OL,11,Fserving politician, Deputy Philip
OL,12,FOzouf, was sentenced to 120 hours
OL,13,Fcommunity service for immigration
OL,14,Foffences.
OL,16,FDeputy Poree believes that the current
OL,17,Flicensing regime for people on
OL,18,Ftemporary permits can expose them to
OL,19,Fmodern slavery practices.
