OL,3,CJersey's migrant workers are at risk
OL,4,Cof being 'kicked into servitude'
OL,6,FShe explains: "I think that the work
OL,7,Fpermit policy, as it stands, is
OL,8,Fkicking workers into servitude.
OL,10,F"37 years ago, when I came to the
OL,11,Fisland, I was free to look for
OL,12,Fdifferent jobs. If my employer didn't
OL,13,Flook after me properly, I had free
OL,14,Fwill.
OL,16,F"Migrant workers - especially the
OL,17,Fseasonal ones - do not have free will."
