OL,3,CJersey's migrant workers are at risk
OL,4,Cof being 'kicked into servitude'
OL,6,FCurrently, those who come to Jersey
OL,7,Ffor work are tied to the employer
OL,8,Fnamed on their licence, meaning they
OL,9,Fcannot leave their job, without
OL,10,Fleaving the island.
OL,12,FDeputy Poree explained: "The employer
OL,13,Fhas control and automony over the
OL,14,Fworker, the worker cannot move unless
OL,15,Fthe employer says so - and often an
OL,16,Femployer would never say so.
OL,26,@tD@Krr
